      主要用于嵌套事务场景 实例：https://jfinal.com/feedback/4008 默认情况下嵌套事务会被合并成为一个事务，那么内层与外层任何地方回滚事务 所有嵌套层都将回滚事务，也就是说嵌套事务无法独立提交与回滚 使用 txInNewThread(...)

        public <T> T queryFirst(String sql,
                        Object... paras)
        Execute sql query and return the first result. I recommend add "limit 1" in your sql.
        参数:
        sql - an SQL statement that may contain one or more '?' IN parameter placeholders
        paras - the parameters of sql
        返回:
        Object[] if your sql has select more than one column, and it return Object if your sql has select only one column.

      • findByIds

        public com.jfinal.plugin.activerecord.Record findByIds(String tableName,
                                                       String primaryKey,
                                                       Object... idValues)
        Find record by ids. 
         Example:
 Record user = Db.use().findByIds("user", "user_id", 123);
 Record userRole = Db.use().findByIds("user_role", "user_id, role_id", 123, 456);
        参数:
        tableName - the table name of the table
        primaryKey - the primary key of the table, composite primary key is separated by comma character: ","
        idValues - the id value of the record, it can be composite id values

      • txInNewThread

        public Future<Boolean> txInNewThread(com.jfinal.plugin.activerecord.IAtom atom)
        主要用于嵌套事务场景 实例：https://jfinal.com/feedback/4008 默认情况下嵌套事务会被合并成为一个事务，那么内层与外层任何地方回滚事务 所有嵌套层都将回滚事务，也就是说嵌套事务无法独立提交与回滚 使用 txInNewThread(...) 方法可以实现层之间的事务控制的独立性 由于事务处理是将 Connection 绑定到线程上的，所以 txInNewThread(...) 通过建立新线程来实现嵌套事务的独立控制

      • batch

        public int[] batch(String sql,
                   Object[][] paras,
                   int batchSize)
        Execute a batch of SQL INSERT, UPDATE, or DELETE queries. 
         Example:
 String sql = "insert into user(name, cash) values(?, ?)";
 int[] result = Db.use().batch(sql, new Object[][]{{"James", 888}, {"zhanjin", 888}});
        参数:
        sql - The SQL to execute.
        paras - An array of query replacement parameters. Each row in this array is one set of batch replacement values.
        返回:
        The number of rows updated per statement
